gn: center;\">2017-12-9 12:48am-10:48pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/my4USGM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fmy4USGM.png&h=ac71398e&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sWB4nSk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsWB4nSk.png&h=41d50bef&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(7)陳嘉寶vs彭慧中(16)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"8b9894cca662a8e8cee714cd20306d303cdcac53","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/491585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/491585</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽已經圓滿結束<br />\n上址為成績公佈,歡迎查看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港女神總會盃第三輪秩序 每日賽事開始時間均為當天凌晨零時<br />\n<br />\n第三圈比賽日1- 2017.12.13<br />\n(乙)湯洛雯vs王敏奕(乙)<br />\n(超)張曦雯vs朱智賢(乙)<br />\n(甲)陳嘉寶vs文詠珊(冠)<br />\n(超)趙慧珊@SGvs游蕙禎(甲)<br />\n(甲)黃智雯vs沈卓盈(冠)<br />\n(超)苟芸慧vs岑麗香(冠)<br />\n(冠)林泳淘vs林穎彤(非)<br />\n(超)朱千雪vs陳穎欣@SG(超)<br />\n<br />\n第三圈比賽日2- 2017.12.14<br />\n(超)謝安琪vs陳法拉(冠)<br />\n(非)陳靜vs簡淑兒(超)<br />\n(甲)劉穎鏇vs簡幗儀(冠)<br />\n(超)李靜儀@SGvs杜小喬(超)<br />\n(超)倪晨曦vs陳嘉倩(超)<br />\n(超)林嘉欣vs鄧麗欣(冠)<br />\n(超)麥明詩vs馮盈盈(超)<br />\n(超)李佳芯vs陳瀅(超)"},{"pid":"db155f3ef00a6bd52456baacfe3ab97546fd6ba0","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268b2b63570f65b56772025fdb7a46f61151418e","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b7a4cfbf479f4b901c0e91efcb98e7b8a3f37c","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d081c64e07db0824f321c496044fc1fce1fa52d8","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fef3cef5cab3d70c12f37fa366268360a1faa0f","tid":493624,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:54:31.000Z","msg":"票已投"},{"pid":"a3e1428a2cad3eebaf808b0a24d9b0a40c82de9a","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4a063f03e2ca1fa41df1ec2b1d575bf1dd05ef","tid":493624,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T23:53:00.0